  lines:
  - speakerName: Silly
    englishSpeakerName: Silly
    text: "\u00D4ng ch\u1EE7 \u0111ang t\u00ECm b\u00E1t \u0103n c\u1EE7a m\u00ECnh, c\u00F3 ph\u1EA3i \u0111\u1ECBnh cho m\u00ECnh \u0103n kh\u00F4ng v\u1EADy, \u0111\u1EC3 m\u00ECnh \u0111i t\u00ECm cho \u00F4ng ch\u1EE7"
    englishText: My owner is looking for my food bowl. Is he going to feed me? I'll go find it for him.
